IREP - Individual-Referential Evaluation Protocol
https://irepprotocol.org - https://github.com/labs-barkley/irep

IREP was initiated by Elodie Aishwarya P. Remoissenet as an open protocol
inspired by her earlier work on individual reference frames and longitudinal
